026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-feature.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-feature.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-feature.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-feature.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-feature.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"4032\" height=\"2268\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Samsung\u0026#39;s Galaxy Watch Ultra, adorning a wrist\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-feature.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-feature.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-galaxy-watch-ultra\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Galaxy Watch Ultra?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003e The Galaxy Watch Ultra comes in just one size at 47mm and features a large and beautiful 1.5-inch AMOLED display that reaches an impressive brightness of 3,000 nits. You also get premium materials on the case with titanium, and the display is protected using sapphire.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eThe combination of these materials means you get a light yet durable smartwatch, which is perfect if you\u0026#39;re looking to take this device outside your typical everyday settings. In addition to the touchscreen, you also get physical buttons for navigation, along with a hotkey that pops on your favorite workout mode with just the push of a button. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eThe watch is powered by Wear OS, which means you\u0026#39;ll get frequent updates that improve the overall experience, along with access to the best apps available. The watch can track health and fitness metrics without breaking a sweat, and also delivers data about sleep quality and stress levels. The battery life is pretty good too, coming in at around two days with normal use. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eAlthough there is \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/samsung-galaxy-watch-ultra-100-gift-card-deal/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea new model of this watch launching soon\u003c/a\u003e, the only difference is that you\u0026#39;re getting more storage with the new watch, which makes this model a far better value at just $325. Be sure to get it now though, because this sale is only going to be around for one more day. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
